Real-Time Example (Banking System)
.....................................
Sealed Class for Payment Types
public sealed class Payment
        permits UpiPayment,
                CardPayment,
                NetBankingPayment {
}
Processing Payment using Pattern Matching
static void process(Payment payment) {

    switch (payment) {

        case UpiPayment u ->
                System.out.println("UPI Payment");

        case CardPayment c ->
                System.out.println("Card Payment");

        case NetBankingPayment n ->
                System.out.println("Net Banking");

    }
}
Output
UPI Payment
